WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.850 --> 00:00:04.830
- My favorite go-to AI tool nowadays

2
00:00:04.830 --> 00:00:06.210
has got to be NotebookLM.

3
00:00:06.210 --> 00:00:08.310
It is such an amazing way

4
00:00:08.310 --> 00:00:10.740
to keep track of all the different things

5
00:00:10.740 --> 00:00:11.880
that I've been meaning to read,

6
00:00:11.880 --> 00:00:13.710
to organize it, to synthesize it,

7
00:00:13.710 --> 00:00:15.030
and give me the key insights I need

8
00:00:15.030 --> 00:00:16.018
to actually get things done.